info.description: I-PR company combine strategy with design and development to help our clients build successful businesses. Our technologies CMS Wordpress, Bitrix, Opencart, Prestashop, frameworks Laravel, Yii2. Have experience for connection websites with ERP system, like SAP, Cloud services, SaaS.  Founded: 2012
